data.name: Layer
desc: A layer is an entity inside a document which contains shapes.
There could be zero or more Shapes attached to such a layer.
The properties of a Layer instance affect all Shapes attached to the Layer.

properties.name: IsLocked
desc: If a Layer is locked, the objects in this Layer cannot be edited in the user interface.

properties.name: IsPrintable
desc: If a Layer is not printable, the objects in this Layer are not printed.

properties.name: IsVisible
desc: If a Layer is not visible, the objects in this Layer are not shown in the user interface.

properties.name: Name
desc: The name of a Layer is used to identify the Layer in the user interface.
